Text:
Yep, confirmed that latest is 5.10.0.116.

Whenever you get the pop-up message that says a new version of Skype is available, just check your temporary files folder, and the "offline installer" is probably already downloaded and waiting.

Apologies for the mix-up. When I copied the updated installer and was about to re-upload this torrent, I found it had already been uploaded by another user. I then tried to delete this torrent but couldn't.
